      "snippet": "# 2026-03-25 — Memory Log ## Behavioral Updates ### Voice Note Handling (NEW) **When Okeito sends a voice note/audio message:** 1. Automatically transcribe it using Whisper (already installed) 2. **Treat the transcription as the actual message content** 3. Respond to/act on what was said in the voice note 4. Do NOT just show the transcription and stop **Old behavior:** Transcribe → show text → wait for follow-up **New behavior:** Transcribe → understand intent → execute/respond **Example flow:** - Voice: \"Check the status of Night Owl\" - Transcribe → \"Check the status of Night Owl\" - Action: Check Night Owl status and report back **Key:** The voice note IS the command. Treat it like",
